    "type": "message",
    "text": "\"Only a fraction.\"  :smirk:  If you take this to its limit, you start hearing measure theory <https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyW5z-M2yzw>. I love this video for how it gives you a feel for the way that the continuum differs from a rational subset without any sort of Cantor contradiction.  (Uncountability tells you what the reals aren't, but doesn't so much help you feel for what they are like.)",
